---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import infrastructureImage from '../../public/infastructure-image.png';
---

<section id="infrastructure" class="px-4 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 space-y-8 md:space-y-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <span class="text-orange-500 font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm uppercase block mb-8">YOUR INFRASTRUCTURE, YOUR RULES</span>
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl xl:text-7xl font-bold">AI That Runs Where Your Data Already Lives</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Encrypted & Isolated</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">Deployed in German or European data centers with enterprise encryption. No public internet exposure.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Connected to Your Systems</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">Integrates directly with your internal documents, APIs, and databases. No data migration required.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Audit-Ready by Default</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">Complete GDPR documentation, role-based access logs, and DPA/NDA included with every deployment.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Built for Your Workflows</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">Every solution is tailored to your processes, your data, and your team, not a generic template.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Production in Weeks</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">From first call to working system in 4-8 weeks. No 18-month enterprise rollouts.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">No Lock-In. Ever.</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold">Open-source foundations mean you own your models, your data, and your infrastructure. Walk away anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    <Image src={infrastructureImage} alt="GDPR-compliant private AI infrastructure diagram showing European cloud deployment and data sovereignty" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg" width={1200} height={800} loading="lazy" />
  </div>
</section>
